<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٣٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُسْتَبْصِرِينَ}</span> ... عَارِفِينَ بِكُفْرِهِمْ مُعْجَبِينَ بِهِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٣٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَمَا كَانُوا سَابِقِينَ}</span> ... فَائِتِينَ مِنْ عَذَابِ اللهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٤٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَخَذْنَا بِذَنبِهِ}</span> ... أَخَذْنَا المَذْكُورِينَ بِعَذَابِنَا بِسَبَبِ ذُنُوبِهِمْ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٤٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَاصِبًا}</span> ... حِجَارَةً مِنْ طِينٍ مَنْضُودٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٤٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الصَّيْحَةُ}</span> ... صَوْتٌ مِنَ السَّمَاءِ مُهْلِكٌ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
