<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٤٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَمَا يَعْقِلُهَا}</span> ... يَتَدَبَّرُهَا، وَيَفْهَمُهَا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٤٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَكْبَرُ}</span> ... أَعْظَمُ وَأَفْضَلُ مِنْ كُلِّ شَيْءٍ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٤٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ظَلَمُوا مِنْهُمْ}</span> ... عَانَدُوا الحَقَّ، وَأَعْلَنُوا الحَرْبَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
